yTime":"2018-02-19T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"飲奶大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會跟晒張相，係我自己聯想鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b5389b145bafb2a1ef69498b241f3cf673161d","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"c456ee72d98d4e5a7aa23ca07bd1b3fa600e5696","tid":565862,"uid":88887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/193506_4d616d207ec7e4ddd477a445f50ac52f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F193506_4d616d207ec7e4ddd477a445f50ac52f.png&h=5ce048b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"已經懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n                           黑人問<br />\n                    問號           黑人<br />\n                 黑人                    問號<br />\n                                           黑人<br />\n                                           問題<br />\n                                     黑人<br />\n                                 問號<br />\n                                 黑<br />\n                                 人<br />\n<br />\n                                 問"},{"pid":"43d83e9c2d04200407955ceaabfbabf8221aeede","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d80d080b484aca8f690edebce7fb95baf209caf9","tid":565862,"uid":78622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png&h=32746489&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"這夜，他獨自一人撐起傘，在一橦橦冰冷的工廠大廈間遊走。他分不清臉上的水的滴是來自那沒有感情的建築物，還是自己淚水。<br />\n<br />\n立秋與寧兒在同一橦大廈工作，每日一同加班，他對她，早已萌生愛意，就只差個機會。<br />\n<br />\n又一個加班深夜，那天立秋靈機一動問寧兒：「今日放工，有冇帶遮？落雨喎。」<br />\n<br />\n「落雨？冇理由架喎，窗外面都....」立秋打斷寧兒：「係落雨呀，今晚一齊走。我有帶遮。」<br />\n<br />\n「哦，好呀。」雖心中有疑惑，但寧兒沒再多想，專心再埋首工作。<br />\n<br />\n他帶她走進大廈的橫街窄巷，徐徐打開雨傘。望著高處一滴滴掉下來的冷氣機水滴，寧兒好似明白了什麼。兩人撐著傘，愈走愈近。<br />\n<br />\n這是觀塘獨有的境像，或是工廠區獨有的境像，更是兩人獨有的天地。<br />\n<br />\n「而家咁興去海山樓影相，但都唔及呢條淨係屬於我地兩個人既祕道咁靚。」立秋露出勝利的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n「夜晚喺兩橦咁高既大廈之間行，覺得自己好渺小。」立秋又說。<br />\n<br />\n「係，人真係好渺少。」寧兒回話。"},{"pid":"46c8415bee2278b844fbd8305213dc131a9bd0a4","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"差住先 仲有冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58886efc03c27debb3aca96e0130b48c6cc667dd","tid":565862,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"6901a67b19b11138826c52ae9a0bd64f834970da","tid":565862,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d83e9c2d04200407955ceaabfbabf8221aeede","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d80d080b484aca8f690edebce7fb95baf209caf9","tid":565862,"uid":78622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png&h=32746489&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"這夜，他獨自一人撐起傘，在一橦橦冰冷的工廠大廈間遊走。他分不清臉上的水的滴是來自那沒有感情的建築物，還是自己淚水。<br />\n<br />\n立秋與寧兒在同一橦大廈工作，每日一同加班，他對她，早已萌生愛意，就只差個機會。<br />\n<br />\n又一個加班深夜，那天立秋靈機一動問寧兒：「今日放工，有冇帶遮？落雨喎。」<br />\n<br />\n「落雨？冇理由架喎，窗外面都....」立秋打斷寧兒：「係落雨呀，今晚一齊走。我有帶遮。」<br />\n<br />\n「哦，好呀。」雖心中有疑惑，但寧兒沒再多想，專心再埋首工作。<br />\n<br />\n他帶她走進大廈的橫街窄巷，徐徐打開雨傘。望著高處一滴滴掉下來的冷氣機水滴，寧兒好似明白了什麼。兩人撐著傘，愈走愈近。<br />\n<br />\n這是觀塘獨有的境像，或是工廠區獨有的境像，更是兩人獨有的天地。<br />\n<br />\n「而家咁興去海山樓影相，但都唔及呢條淨係屬於我地兩個人既祕道咁靚。」立秋露出勝利的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n「夜晚喺兩橦咁高既大廈之間行，覺得自己好渺小。」立秋又說。<br />\n<br />\n「係，人真係好渺少。」寧兒回話。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"「係，人真係好渺少。」寧兒回話。<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢句 嘆氣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfadc3ded801ff3f5ea5c4426f836367f0ae8a4","tid":565862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/193506_4d616d207ec7e4ddd477a445f50ac52f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F193506_4d616d207ec7e4ddd477a445f50ac52f.png&h=5ce048b3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>已經懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n                           黑人問<br />\n                    問號           黑人<br />\n                 黑人                    問號<br />\n                                           黑人<br />\n                                           問題<br />\n                                     黑人<br />\n                                 問號<br />\n                                 黑<br />\n                                 人<br />\n<br />\n                                 問</blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebf9ae9118624a9b1514d0e69429eab147e2e8a","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfcc4161f9dc7d073709391ebb8d0c9018069aca","tid":565862,"uid":36084,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20080130/large/30la1p104new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080130%2Flarge%2F30la1p104new.jpg&h=82a34da9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"呀詩一直是個堅定的女權分子，深信男人可做的，女人也有權利去做。於是她決定身體力行，以百人斬男人作為目標，積極享受性愛，誓要食盡天下男人。<br />\n<br />\n每次跟男人上床後，都會拍照留念，甚至跟朋友分享戰績，與哪個男神有一腿，跟哪個女人的丈夫有一夜情。朋友除了配服她之外，心底裡對她的行為仍有點保留。不過她一於少理，男人以此為樂，以此逞威風，她為何不可？<br />\n<br />\n別家大學一個男生風頭躉流出床照，一個又一個床上對手女生在網上及大學間瘋傳，呀詩是其中一個女生。<br />\n<br />\n她原先不以為然，誰知道回到學校，同學都在暗地裡討論她或笑她。呀詩完全不明白，好像她過去的戰績不復存在，就連朋友也認為她有點可憐。明明是「老煉的牛肺」，卻慘被人話「天真」，才是最大的侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n她討厭本是你情我願的事，甚至是她作主動，但現在卻慘被套上「受害者」的角色。事與願違，原來人們都是比較愛看男人風流。"},{"pid":"114237a5da4737bb652d2cd7cedbbdca4d2c770e","tid":565862,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/234215_beee661f1973e9a47dd08d460ce1dfd2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F234215_beee661f1973e9a47dd08d460ce1dfd2.JPG&h=90924de7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a140ad282e72e28de0b8bb844eabd3492827a23c","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6901a67b19b11138826c52ae9a0bd64f834970da","tid":565862,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d83e9c2d04200407955ceaabfbabf8221aeede","tid":565862,"uid":65158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d80d080b484aca8f690edebce7fb95baf209caf9","tid":565862,"uid":78622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F193514_120fa0a69265f85cc6c65abb3dd7c4d5.png&h=32746489&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"這夜，他獨自一人撐起傘，在一橦橦冰冷的工廠大廈間遊走。他分不清臉上的水的滴是來自那沒有感情的建築物，還是自己淚水。<br />\n<br />\n立秋與寧兒在同一橦大廈工作，每日一同加班，他對她，早已萌生愛意，就只差個機會。<br />\n<br />\n又一個加班深夜，那天立秋靈機一動問寧兒：「今日放工，有冇帶遮？落雨喎。」<br />\n<br /